Enclave at Boxborough is active-adult, 55+ community located in the town center of the prestigious town of Boxborough, MA. Offering carriage-style townhome designs with two-story and single-story living, all with first-floor primary bedroom suites and 2-car garages. With its outstanding location and resort-style amenities, Enclave at Boxborough is set to be the premier active adult community in Boxborough. Virtually tour and explore the Davis home design at TollBrothers.com/MA. 
#LoveEverythingAboutHome

Residents will enjoy the ultimate Florida lifestyle at the private, staffed Residents' Club with a state-of-the-art fitness center, resort-style pool, and tennis courts. Virtually tour and explore the Callahan home design on TollBrothers.com/FL. 
#LoveEverythingAboutHome
